# 🧴 Cosmetic Innovation Watcher

An Apify actor that monitors cosmetic and health innovations worldwide.

## 📌 Objective

Automatically track new cosmetic/health products in:
- R&D phase
- Clinical tests
- Pre-launch
- Press announcements

## ✨ Features

- ✅ Multi-source scraping (News, Press Releases, Databases)
- ✅ Company data enrichment with LinkedIn
- ✅ Automatic CSV/JSON export
- ✅ Daily scheduling
- ✅ International coverage (France priority)

## 📊 Data Collected

For each product:
1. Product name
2. Description
3. Type (cosmetic, dermo, biotech, etc.)
4. Estimated launch date
5. Company/Laboratory
6. Country
7. Source
8. Contact information (LinkedIn, Email, Phone)

## 🗺️ Coverage

- 🇫🇷 France (Priority)
- 🌍 International (USA, UK, Germany, Asia, etc.)

## 🚀 Quick Start

### Installation

\`\`\`bash
git clone https://github.com/tcarlino-del/cosmetic-innovation-watcher.git
cd cosmetic-innovation-watcher
npm install
\`\`\`

### Local Run

\`\`\`bash
npm start
\`\`\`

### Deploy to Apify

\`\`\`bash
apify push
\`\`\`

## 📋 Configuration

Edit \`.env\` file:

\`\`\`env
PROXYCURL_API_KEY=your_key
MAX_REQUESTS_PER_SOURCE=50
\`\`\`

